Now go to Player.java and add this next to the other delays:
[code]
diceDelay
[/code]

Go to Dialoguehandler.java and underneath the other dialogues add this:
[code]
case 94:
sendOption4("Dice (Up to 100)", "Dice (10 sided)", "Dice (6 sided)", "Dice (Black-Jack)");
c.dialogueAction = 16;
c.dialogueId = 94;
break;
[/code]

Go to Clickingbuttons.java and under case 9178 add this:
[code]
if (c.dialogueAction == 16) {
c.getItems().deleteItem(15084,1);
c.getItems().addItem(15098,1);
c.getPA().removeAllWindows();
}
[/code]
And this under case 9179:
[code]
if (c.dialogueAction == 16) {
c.getItems().deleteItem(15084,1);
c.getItems().addItem(15092,1);
c.getPA().removeAllWindows();
}
[/code]
And this under case 9180:
[code]
if (c.dialogueAction == 16) {
c.getItems().deleteItem(15084,1);
c.getItems().addItem(15086,1);
c.getPA().removeAllWindows();
}
[/code]
And finally this under case 9181:
[code]
if (c.dialogueAction == 16) {
c.getItems().deleteItem(15084,1);
c.getItems().addItem(15088,1);
c.getPA().removeAllWindows();
}
[/code]

Add this into Itemclick3.java:
